Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\be5}YA NE U RA NO NE KO\N{\i0\be0}The cat in the attic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HA0E4E6&}\h\h\h\h\h\h\hga\N{\r}Since it's "me becomes ne"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It makes sense if we change the "me" to "ne" and then read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was the trick behind the demon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None other than that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother collapsed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she snuck out of her futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when Takako-san heard a strange sound\Nfrom the hallway and came to this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had already collapsed in front of the bureau?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only went to the restroom for a short while...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are some things rolling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're prayer beads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's grasping onto eight beads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the fourth one from her thumb is a small heavenly bead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beads...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that folklore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, Satomi-san already knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which of these people is the serial murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha-chan, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you come to the restroom with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you at least go to the loo by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were just attacked by the demon dog in the backyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We shudder at the thought that it may\Nappear inside the house this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why are you awake, my brave sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's bothering you too, right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw the demon dog after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the brat with glasses and the detective kid from Osaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are sleeping without a care in the world, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because they said something like they knew who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They figured out the culprit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying they figured out the serial killer\Nwho's mixed in with the adopted children?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although they wouldn't tell us who.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed they were able to discern some clues after\Nhearing about the names of the adopted children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hearing about their names?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1\shad0\bord1.2\b1\fscy140\fscx140\fad(420,420)\fncalibri\pos(192.429,236.468)}TAMA    KI
