Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1\shad0\bord1.2\b1\fscy140\fscx140\fad(420,420)\fncalibri\pos(193.288,235.896)}YUU    KA
